Package gg.valgo.gradian.util.coroutine

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoroutineExecutor<ReturnType>
    An interface representing a lambda for the coroutine execution.
    CoroutineYieldConsumer<ResultType>
    An interface which represents a function that consumed yielded values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coroutine<ResultType>
    A coroutine, used internally by the coroutine parser.
    CoroutineContext<ResultType>
    A context passed to a Coroutine executor with a yield() and reject() method.
    CoroutineExecutionContext
    Represents the execution context of a coroutine in a coroutine parser.
    CoroutineResult<ResultType>
    The result of a coroutine.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CoroutineExitException
    An exception used to break out of a coroutine.
